Write tests for NmonApp in tests/test_app.py. The test file should import NmonApp from nmon.app, and all other modules under test from their production location. Do not redefine or copy-paste the classes/functions under test into the test file.

The NmonApp class has these key methods and behaviors to test:
- NmonApp.__init__() initializes with correct settings and monitors
- NmonApp.start() starts cleanly with proper resource setup
- NmonApp.stop() stops cleanly with proper resource cleanup
- NmonApp._probe_ollama() detects Ollama presence correctly
