   - history_store: HistoryStore
   - settings: Settings
   - prefs: UserPrefs
8. Run NmonApp's event loop via app.run()
9. On Ctrl+C or SIGTERM, gracefully shut down all monitors and flush history to DB
10. Handle pynvml init failure by raising SystemExit

The main function should follow the pseudocode in the architecture plan and handle all error conditions as specified in the error handling section. Use proper imports and type annotations as defined in the module's data model cross-reference.

